  <section class="mb-8">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-100 mb-4">The DISC model measures and describes four foundational styles:</h2>
    <ol class="list-decimal pl-6 mb-8 space-y-2">
      <li class="text-gray-100">Dominance</li>
      <li class="text-gray-100">Influence</li>
      <li class="text-gray-100">Steadiness</li>
      <li class="text-gray-100">Compliance</li>
    </ol>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-8">
    <p class="text-gray-100 mb-4">Please see a description of each style below that might help you identify the personality style of the person you work with.</p>
